{"cells":[{"source":"<p align="center"><img src='images/redpopcorn.jpg' alt="Red popcorn Netflix project image" width="500"></p>","metadata":{},"id":"937acf3c-c077-4ca6-8d90-8f6dd4d13c54","cell_type":"markdown"},{"source":"**Netflix**! What started in 1997 as a DVD rental service has since exploded into one of the largest entertainment and media companies.\n\nGiven the large number of movies and series available on the platform, it is a perfect opportunity to showcase my exploratory data analysis skills and dive into the entertainment industry.\n\nIn this project, I analyze Netflix data to explore movies released in the 1990s. Working from the perspective of a production company focused on nostalgic content, the goal is to identify patterns in genre, runtime, and overall film characteristics. This exploratory data analysis provides insight into the trends that defined the decade and can inform future content strategy.\n\nI have been supplied with the dataset `netflix_data.csv`, along with the following table detailing the column names and descriptions. \n\n## The data\n### **netflix_data.csv**\n| Column | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `show_id` | The ID of the show |\n| `type` | Type of show |\n| `title` | Title of the show |\n| `director` | Director of the show |\n| `cast` | Cast of the show |\n| `country` | Country of origin |\n| `date_added` | Date added to Netflix |\n| `release_year` | Year of Netflix release |\n| `duration` | Duration of the show in minutes |\n| `description` | Description of the show |\n| `genre` | Show genre |","metadata":{},"id":"5962b2cd-17bb-4ec9-b2d5-68537ca26860","cell_type":"markdown"},{"source":"#Importing pandas and matplotlib\nimport pandas as pd\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n#Read in the Netflix CSV as a DataFrame\nnetflix_df = pd.read_csv(\"netflix_data.csv\")\n\n#Filter for movies only\nmovies = netflix_df[netflix_df[\"type\"] == \"Movie\"]\n\n#Filter for movies released in the 1990s\nmovies_1990s = movies[(movies[\"release_year\"] >= 1990) & (movies[\"release_year\"] <= 1999)]\n\n#Create the duration variable (required for some questions)\nduration = int(movies_1990s[\"duration\"].mode()[0])\n\n#Count short movies\nshort_movie_count = int(\n    movies_1990s[\n        (movies_1990s[\"genre\"] == \"Action\") &\n        (movies_1990s[\"duration\"] < 90)\n    ].shape[0]\n)\n\nprint(f\"Most common movie duration in the 1990s: {duration} minutes\")\nprint(f\"Number of short Action movies (<90 min): {short_movie_count}\")","metadata":{"executionTime":2854,"lastSuccessfullyExecutedCode":"#Importing pandas and matplotlib\nimport pandas as pd\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n\n#Read in the Netflix CSV as a DataFrame\nnetflix_df = pd.read_csv(\"netflix_data.csv\")\n\n#Filter for movies only\nmovies = netflix_df[netflix_df[\"type\"] == \"Movie\"]\n\n#Filter for movies released in the 1990s\nmovies_1990s = movies[(movies[\"release_year\"] >= 1990) & (movies[\"release_year\"] <= 1999)]\n\n#Create the duration variable (required for some questions)\nduration = int(movies_1990s[\"duration\"].mode()[0])\n\n#Count short movies\nshort_movie_count = int(\n    movies_1990s[\n        (movies_1990s[\"genre\"] == \"Action\") &\n        (movies_1990s[\"duration\"] < 90)\n    ].shape[0]\n)\n\nprint(f\"Most common movie duration in the 1990s: {duration} minutes\")\nprint(f\"Number of short Action movies (<90 min): {short_movie_count}\")","executionCancelledAt":null,"lastExecutedAt":1776083659185,"lastExecutedByKernel":"ba5e0d02-734d-4d58-941c-de5da924b908","lastScheduledRunId":null,"outputsMetadata":{"0":{"height":56,"type":"stream"}}},"id":"320a3abc-8a36-4b2b-baaf-473325363a4d","cell_type":"code","execution_count":2,"outputs":[{"output_type":"stream","name":"stdout","text":"Most common movie duration in the 1990s: 94 minutes\nNumber of short Action movies (<90 min): 7\n"}]},{"source":"#Distribution of movie durations (1990–1999)\n\nplt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n\nplt.hist(\n    movies_1990s[\"duration\"],\n    bins=20,\n    edgecolor=\"black\",\n    alpha=0.8\n)\n\nplt.title(\"Distribution of Movie Durations (1990–1999)\", fontsize=14)\nplt.xlabel(\"Duration (Minutes)\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Number of Movies\")\n\nplt.grid(axis=\"y\", linestyle=\"--\", alpha=0.6)\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()","metadata":{"executionCancelledAt":null,"executionTime":407,"lastExecutedAt":1776083661722,"lastExecutedByKernel":"ba5e0d02-734d-4d58-941c-de5da924b908","lastScheduledRunId":null,"lastSuccessfullyExecutedCode":"#Distribution of movie durations (1990–1999)\n\nplt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n\nplt.hist(\n    movies_1990s[\"duration\"],\n    bins=20,\n    edgecolor=\"black\",\n    alpha=0.8\n)\n\nplt.title(\"Distribution of Movie Durations (1990–1999)\", fontsize=14)\nplt.xlabel(\"Duration (Minutes)\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Number of Movies\")\n\nplt.grid(axis=\"y\", linestyle=\"--\", alpha=0.6)\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()"},"cell_type":"code","id":"fa7668d2-96c2-4d8f-bc3e-353e3ab5fa6d","outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1000x600 with 1 Axes>","image/png":""},"metadata":{"image/png":{"width":988,"height":589}}}],"execution_count":3},{"source":"#Most common genres among movies released between 1990 and 1999\n\ntop_genres = (\n    movies_1990s[\"genre\"]\n    .value_counts()\n    .rename_axis(\"Genre\")\n    .rename(\"Number of Movies\")\n    .reset_index()\n)\n\ntop_genre_counts.head().style.set_table_styles(\n    [{\"selector\": \"table\", \"props\": [(\"margin-left\", \"auto\"), (\"margin-right\", \"auto\")]}]\n).hide(axis=\"index\")","metadata":{"executionCancelledAt":null,"executionTime":16,"lastExecutedAt":1776083713138,"lastExecutedByKernel":"ba5e0d02-734d-4d58-941c-de5da924b908","lastScheduledRunId":null,"lastSuccessfullyExecutedCode":"#Most common genres among movies released between 1990 and 1999\n\ntop_genres = (\n    movies_1990s[\"genre\"]\n    .value_counts()\n    .rename_axis(\"Genre\")\n    .rename(\"Number of Movies\")\n    .reset_index()\n)\n\ntop_genre_counts.head().style.set_table_styles(\n    [{\"selector\": \"table\", \"props\": [(\"margin-left\", \"auto\"), (\"margin-right\", \"auto\")]}]\n).hide(axis=\"index\")","outputsMetadata":{"0":{"height":552,"type":"dataFrame","tableState":{"customFilter":{"const":{"type":"boolean","valid":true,"value":true},"id":"83e4456a-8096-46f1-8f25-9486163e0dd8","nodeType":"const"}}}}},"cell_type":"code","id":"17573a82-dbbc-4398-8a0e-2365041216a2","outputs":[{"output_type":"execute_result","data":{"text/plain":"<pandas.io.formats.style.Styler at 0x7f04de3e98b0>","text/html":"<style type=\"text/css\">\n#T_f8acc table {\n  margin-left: auto;\n  margin-right: auto;\n}\n</style>\n<table id=\"T_f8acc\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th id=\"T_f8acc_level0_col0\" class=\"col_heading level0 col0\" >Genre</th>\n      <th id=\"T_f8acc_level0_col1\" class=\"col_heading level0 col1\" >Number of Movies</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row0_col0\" class=\"data row0 col0\" >Action</td>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row0_col1\" class=\"data row0 col1\" >48</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row1_col0\" class=\"data row1 col0\" >Dramas</td>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row1_col1\" class=\"data row1 col1\" >44</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row2_col0\" class=\"data row2 col0\" >Comedies</td>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row2_col1\" class=\"data row2 col1\" >40</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row3_col0\" class=\"data row3 col0\" >Children</td>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row3_col1\" class=\"data row3 col1\" >15</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row4_col0\" class=\"data row4 col0\" >Classic Movies</td>\n      <td id=\"T_f8acc_row4_col1\" class=\"data row4 col1\" >15</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n"},"metadata":{},"execution_count":8}],"execution_count":8},{"source":"**Observation**\n\nThe most common genre of Movies released between 1990 and 1999 are action, dramas, and comedies, suggesting that character-driven stories and lighter entertainment were especially prominent during these years.","metadata":{},"cell_type":"markdown","id":"774a84d3-bb5c-4295-872b-ae7d3b6e4ddd"},{"source":"plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n\nplt.bar(\n    top_genres[\"Genre\"],\n    top_genres[\"Number of Movies\"]\n)\n\nplt.title(\"Top Genres of Movies Released Between 1990 and 1999\", fontsize=14)\nplt.xlabel(\"Genre\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Number of Movies\")\n\nplt.xticks(rotation=45, ha=\"right\")\nplt.grid(axis=\"y\", linestyle=\"--\", alpha=0.6)\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()","metadata":{"executionCancelledAt":null,"executionTime":267,"lastExecutedAt":1776083733818,"lastExecutedByKernel":"ba5e0d02-734d-4d58-941c-de5da924b908","lastScheduledRunId":null,"lastSuccessfullyExecutedCode":"plt.figure(figsize=(10,6))\n\nplt.bar(\n    top_genres[\"Genre\"],\n    top_genres[\"Number of Movies\"]\n)\n\nplt.title(\"Top Genres of Movies Released Between 1990 and 1999\", fontsize=14)\nplt.xlabel(\"Genre\")\nplt.ylabel(\"Number of Movies\")\n\nplt.xticks(rotation=45, ha=\"right\")\nplt.grid(axis=\"y\", linestyle=\"--\", alpha=0.6)\n\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()"},"cell_type":"code","id":"2942c562-93eb-46ee-bf3b-1f736651d977","outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1000x600 with 1 Axes>","image/png":""},"metadata":{"image/png":{"width":988,"height":588}}}],"execution_count":10},{"source":"## Conclusion\n\nThe movies released between 1990 and 1999 on Netflix usually run just under two hours. \n\nThe average duration is about 115 minutes, while the median duration is 108 minutes, indicating that most films fall close to this range. \n\nMovie lengths vary widely, from a minimum of 28 minutes to a maximum of 195 minutes, suggesting that while most films cluster around the two-hour mark, there are some much shorter and longer titles in the dataset.\n\nThe exploratory analysis of Netflix movies released between 1990 and 1999 shows that the decade includes a substantial number of films with varied genres and runtimes. \n\nThe duration analysis indicates that most movies are around two hours long, with an average runtime of about 115 minutes and a median of 108 minutes. While most films cluster near this typical length, the dataset also includes shorter and longer titles, showing a wide range of movie durations. \n\nThis analysis provides a clearer understanding of the characteristics of movies from the 1990s available on Netflix.","metadata":{},"cell_type":"markdown","id":"397149fa-c18c-4dc1-9206-48a19f75541d"}],"metadata":{"colab":{"name":"Welcome to DataCamp Workspaces.ipynb","provenance":[]},"kernelspec":{"display_name":"Python 3 (ipykernel)","language":"python","name":"python3"},"language_info":{"name":"python","version":"3.8.10","mimetype":"text/x-python","codemirror_mode":{"name":"ipython","version":3},"pygments_lexer":"ipython3","nbconvert_exporter":"python","file_extension":".py"},"editor":"DataLab"},"nbformat":4,"nbformat_minor":5}
